                "Measurements As Well As Uncertainties Introduced by",
                "The Differentiating Procedure Applied in the Analysis",
                "Of the Experimental Data.Furthermore the Uncertainties",
                "In the Stopping Power,in the Detector Efficiency and in",
                "The Current Integration are Also Included."
